def get_all_data(stock_id):
    lrb_xq = pd.read_csv(
        r'data/%s_lrb.csv' % (stock_id),
        encoding='utf-8',
        header=0,
        index_col=None)
    fzb_xq = pd.read_csv(
        r'data/%s_fzb.csv' % (stock_id),
        encoding='utf-8',
        header=0,
        index_col=None)
    llb_xq = pd.read_csv(
        r'data/%s_llb.csv' % (stock_id),
        encoding='utf-8',
        header=0,
        index_col=None)

    list_lrb = []
    for i in lrb_xq['']:
        str_i = str(i)
        # i_ = i[:4] + '-' + i[4:6] + '-' + i[6:8]
        list_lrb.append(str(i))
    list_lrb_0 = []
    for i in list_lrb:
        i_ = i[:4] + '-' + i[4:6] + '-' + i[6:8]
        list_lrb_0.append(i_)
    list_fzb = []
    for i in fzb_xq['']:
        str_i = str(i)
        # i_ = i[:4] + '-' + i[4:6] + '-' + i[6:8]
        list_fzb.append(str_i)
    list_fzb_0 = []
    for i in list_fzb:
        i_ = i[:4] + '-' + i[4:6] + '-' + i[6:8]
        list_fzb_0.append(i_)
    list_llb = []
    for i in llb_xq['']:
        str_i = str(i)
        # i_ = i[:4] + '-' + i[4:6] + '-' + i[6:8]
        list_llb.append(str_i)
    list_llb_0 = []
    for i in list_llb:
        i_ = i[:4] + '-' + i[4:6] + '-' + i[6:8]
        list_llb_0.append(i_)

    lrb_xq[''] = [pd.to_datetime(t) for t in list_lrb_0]
    fzb_xq[''] = [pd.to_datetime(t) for t in list_fzb_0]
    llb_xq[''] = [pd.to_datetime(t) for t in list_llb_0]

    data_temp = pd.merge(lrb_xq, fzb_xq, how='left', on='')
    data = pd.merge(data_temp, llb_xq, how='left', on='')

    data.index = data['']

    data = data[::-1]
    return data

def get_data_month(data, month):
    data_month = data[data.index.month == month]
    return data_month

def get_data_ratio(data):
    result = pd.DataFrame()
    result[''] = data[''] / data['']
    result[''] = (data[''] - data['']) / data['']
    result[''] = (
        data[''] + data[''] + data['_x']) / data['']
    result[''] = data[''] / data['']
    result[''] = data[''] / data['']
    result[''] = data['_x'] / data['']
    result['ROE'] = data[''] / data['']
    result[''] = data[''] / data['']
    result[''] = 365 * data[''] / data['']
    result[''] = data[''] / data['']
    result[''] = data[''].pct_change(axis=0)
    result[''] = data[''].pct_change(axis=0)
    
    result[''] = data['']
    result[''] = data['']
    result[''] = data['']
    result[''] = data['']
    result[''] = data['']
    
    result[''] = data['']
    result[''] = data[''] / 1e8
    result[''] = data[''] / 1e8
    result.index = data['']
    return result

def data_plot(data, ratio, legend, kind='bar'):
    l_0 = len(data)
    s_0 = list(range(l_0))
    x_0 = np.array(s_0)
    y_0 = tuple([str(i) for i in range(year - l_0, year)])
    
    data[ratio].plot(kind=kind)
    plt.title(ratio)
#     plt.ylabel(ratio)
#     plt.legend([legend], loc='upper left')
    plt.legend([legend])
    plt.xticks(x_0, y_0)
    plt.grid(color='#95a5a6', linestyle='--', linewidth=1, axis='y',alpha=0.4)
    plt.savefig(r'pic/%s.png' % (ratio,))
#     plt.show();
    return

def multi_plot(ratio):
    fig = plt.figure()
    fig.set_figheight(4)
    fig.set_figwidth(24)

    plt.subplot(141)
    data_plot(result_0, ratio, '')
    plt.subplot(142)
    data_plot(result_1, ratio, '')
    plt.subplot(143)
    data_plot(result_2, ratio, '')
    plt.subplot(144)
    data_plot(result_3, ratio, '')
    plt.show();
    return

def ratio_compare(ratio):
    s = pd.DataFrame()
    s['ratio_0'] = result_0[ratio]
    s['ratio_1'] = result_1[ratio]
    s['ratio_2'] = result_2[ratio]
    s['ratio_3'] = result_3[ratio]
    s.index = result_0.index 

    s.plot(kind='line')
    plt.title('%s' % (ratio, ))
    plt.ylabel(ratio)
#     plt.legend(['', '', '', ''], loc='upper right')
    plt.legend(['', '', '', ''])
    plt.grid(color='#95a5a6', linestyle='--', linewidth=1, axis='y',alpha=0.4)
    plt.savefig(r'pic/%s.png' % (ratio,))
    plt.show();
    return
